This paper proposes a new algorithm for improving the performance of Bloom filters by incorporating a machine learning model as a binary classifier. The paper focuses on the efficiency of the classifier and its utilization in the learned Bloom filter. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DB (Databases), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
